Spain coach Robert Moreno has challenged Dani Ceballos to seize his opportunity at Arsenal and play a lot, saying the most important thing for all his players is regular game time.<br />
<br />
&quot;What I want is for him to play, the important thing is that the players have minutes.&quot;

Former Arsenal captain Thomas Vermaelen:<br />
<br />
&quot;Arsenal have done well with the players they got in the window. I expect a lot from Arsenal and I always hope they do well. I expect Arsenal will do better than last year.&quot;
